cycle The Watch Rotation

circle-nodes

Morning Watch blue
  Fresh hands take the wheel at dawn.

Forenoon Watch green
  Scrub the decks and mend the sails.

Afternoon Watch yellow
  Splice lines and keep a sharp lookout.

Dog Watch orange
  Short shifts so no crew stands the same
  hours two nights running.

Night Watch purple
  Steer by the stars till the morning
  hands relieve the deck.
